    Gold Peace Pendant

    Only 1 left in stock

    Log in to save your wishlist.

    Please login
    SHARE Share on Facebook Pin on Pinterest

    Full Description

    Our large hammered gold Peace pendant makes a bold statement and eye-catching accessory.

    We have introduced the iconic Peace symbol into our 18 carat gold plated jewellery collection as a mindful reminder to ourselves that true peace arises from within. Designed in 1958 by British pacifist and graphic artist Gerald Holtom for the CND movement, over the years the symbol has come to be recognised as standing for peace and justice across the globe.

    • Ethically Handmade in Turkey
    • 18ct Gold Plated

    Shipping and Returns

    DELIVERY
